<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Khumalo Craft</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center:
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e67e22;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Us - Khumalo Craft</h1>

        <header>

            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>Welcome to Khumalo CraftMarketplace, where creativity meets craftsmanship. We are passionate about connecting talented artists with discerning customers who appreciate unique, handmade products.</p>
                <p>Our journey began in 2010 when our founder, Mr James Khumalo, envisioned a platform where local artists could showcase their skilols and reach a wider audieence. Since then, we have been dedicated to promoting traditional crafsmanship and supporting artisans in growing their businesses.</p>

                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>At Khumal Craft, our mission is to celebrate diversity and cultural heritagte through artisanal craftmanship. We strive to provide a platform where artists can thrive, communities can prosperm and customers can discover beautiful handmamde products that tell a  story.</p>
                <h2>Why choose Khumalo Craft?</h2>
                <p>When you shop with Khumalo Craft, you're not just purchasing a product- you're supporting sustainable livelihoods and preserving cultural traditions.We carefully create our marketplace to ensure that every item is ethically sourced and of the highest quality.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="display-4">Welcome</h1>
                <p>Learn about <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/aspnet/core">building Web apps with ASP.NET Core</a>.</p>
            </div>

            <h2>Welcome to the Home Page!</h2>

            @if (UserID != null)
            {
                <p>User ID: @UserID</p>
            }

            <h2>All Products</h2>

            <table class="table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Name</th>
                        <th>Price</th>
                        <th>Category</th>
                        <th>Availability</th>
                        <th>Action</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    @foreach (var product in Products)
                    {
                        <tr>
                            <td>@product.Name</td>
                            <td>@product.Price</td>
                            <td>@product.Category</td>
                            <td>@product.Availability</td>
                            <td>
                                <form asp-controller="Transaction" asp-action="PlaceOrder" method="post">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="userID" value="@UserID" />
                                    <input type="hidden" name="productID" value="@product.ProductID" />
                                    <button type="submit">Place Order</button>
                                </form>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    }
                </tbody>
            </table>

</body>
            </header>
            </header>




</html>